## 🎯 Project Objective

Financial reporting in the banking sector demands the highest levels of accuracy, compliance, and transparency. Working as the second-in-command (and frequently Acting HOD) in the Finance Department across two development banks, I was responsible for the end-to-end preparation of IFRS/NFRS-compliant financial statements — from monthly management accounts to the prestigious Annual Book (Annual Report) — which was published, distributed to shareholders, and filed with regulators.

